Wonderful design house in Camarma de Esteruelas Engel & Völkers presents this wonderful designer house located in Camarma de Esteruelas. With an area of approximately 231 m2 this house is distributed over 2 floors, providing ample indoor and outdoor spaces. Upon entering, you will be greeted by a bright foyer that will lead you to the main living area. The location of this property is unbeatable. Located in a quiet residential area, it gives you the opportunity to live in a serene and safe environment, away from the hustle and bustle of the city, but with easy access to services, stores and public transport. In short, this is an exceptional design house with the best qualities, located in Camarma de Esteruelas. With its ample spaces, private garden and additional amenities, it offers the perfect environment to enjoy a comfortable and luxurious life. Do not miss the opportunity to make this house your home! Camarma de Esteruelas is a charming town located in the province of Madrid, Spain. It is an ideal place for those looking for a quiet and relaxing environment to establish their home, while enjoying an excellent quality of life. It offers a rural and picturesque atmosphere, surrounded by beautiful natural landscapes and green areas. Here you can enjoy the serenity and tranquility that only a rural environment can provide, away from the hustle and bustle and stress of the city. Despite its rural character, Camarma de Esteruelas has a wide range of services and amenities for its residents. In the center of town, you will find a variety of stores, supermarkets, restaurants and cafes, where you can satisfy all your daily needs. In addition, there are pharmacies, banks and other professional services available. In terms of education, there are nursery schools, schools and high schools, which makes it an excellent choice for families with children. There are also sports centers and parks where you can enjoy outdoor activities and maintain a healthy lifestyle. The town has good transport connections, making it easy to travel to other nearby areas. There are bus lines that connect Camarma de Esteruelas with neighboring towns and with the center of Madrid. In addition, the proximity to the highway facilitates access by car to other areas of the province. If you are a lover of nature and outdoor activities, you will be delighted with the possibilities offered by Camarma de Esteruelas. Its surroundings are full of beautiful rural landscapes, ideal for walking, hiking or cycling. You will also find recreational areas and natural spaces where you can enjoy a day with family or friends.
